  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mac Biskwi Adventures</strong> is a 2D platformer that brings back a nostalgic feeling and offers unique and fun-loving gameplay, with a mix of exploration and adventure. In a very solid and cute way. Fasten your seat belts… it’s time to rescue Mac’s missing girlfriend! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GO ON A JOURNEY OF DISCOVERY THROUGH BISCUIT’S ISLAND</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore different levels with colorful visuals and special routes to be discovered, cross the trees and make your way through Biscuit’s Island while you get rid of evil creatures that are spreading the chaos on the Island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/830aa1cb5864ff0ba11a821f1ddfac63.poster.avif?t=1769088471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/830aa1cb5864ff0ba11a821f1ddfac63.webm?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/830aa1cb5864ff0ba11a821f1ddfac63.mp4?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BISCUITS & GOLDEN TOKENS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure to collect all the biscuits & golden tokens you see! Some might be in hidden places, so don’t forget to explore every single route of each map and don’t leave any collectibles behind!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/fdfac171bc1764ca13948521fa376949.poster.avif?t=1769088471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/fdfac171bc1764ca13948521fa376949.webm?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/fdfac171bc1764ca13948521fa376949.mp4?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COOL VEHICLES!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover a new vehicle available in each level and be prepared for a few surprises… Show your skateboarding skills, ride a shooting tank and even a mecha!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/ad834b56b4e445d75bdde7ba64a22867.poster.avif?t=1769088471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/ad834b56b4e445d75bdde7ba64a22867.webm?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/ad834b56b4e445d75bdde7ba64a22867.mp4?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEAT BIG BOSSES!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll get to beat big bosses at the end of each level! They might look scary and stronger than our little monkey, but Mac is smart! Don’t forget to use walls to jump, avoid their abilities & beat’em up with your weapons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/8a8d18111dae1bfdcb742f8c38d27649.poster.avif?t=1769088471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/8a8d18111dae1bfdcb742f8c38d27649.webm?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/8a8d18111dae1bfdcb742f8c38d27649.mp4?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OVERVIEW</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A colorful and unexpected experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 unique levels and 6 bosses </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different weapons for each level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple and smooth controls: you can use keyboard or a controller</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game modes: Normal and Hard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levels are filled with enemies who can only be defeated by jumping on them or using weapons like a boomerang or a laser gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the true ending by finishing the game in Hard mode!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks to ComiXme for their collaboration in the production of the trailer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mac Biskwi Adventures</strong> is a 2D platformer that brings back a nostalgic feeling and offers unique and fun-loving gameplay, with a mix of exploration and adventure. In a very solid and cute way. Fasten your seat belts… it’s time to rescue Mac’s missing girlfriend! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GO ON A JOURNEY OF DISCOVERY THROUGH BISCUIT’S ISLAND</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore different levels with colorful visuals and special routes to be discovered, cross the trees and make your way through Biscuit’s Island while you get rid of evil creatures that are spreading the chaos on the Island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/830aa1cb5864ff0ba11a821f1ddfac63.poster.avif?t=1769088471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/830aa1cb5864ff0ba11a821f1ddfac63.webm?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/830aa1cb5864ff0ba11a821f1ddfac63.mp4?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BISCUITS & GOLDEN TOKENS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure to collect all the biscuits & golden tokens you see! Some might be in hidden places, so don’t forget to explore every single route of each map and don’t leave any collectibles behind!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/fdfac171bc1764ca13948521fa376949.poster.avif?t=1769088471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/fdfac171bc1764ca13948521fa376949.webm?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/fdfac171bc1764ca13948521fa376949.mp4?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COOL VEHICLES!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover a new vehicle available in each level and be prepared for a few surprises… Show your skateboarding skills, ride a shooting tank and even a mecha!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/ad834b56b4e445d75bdde7ba64a22867.poster.avif?t=1769088471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/ad834b56b4e445d75bdde7ba64a22867.webm?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/ad834b56b4e445d75bdde7ba64a22867.mp4?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEAT BIG BOSSES!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll get to beat big bosses at the end of each level! They might look scary and stronger than our little monkey, but Mac is smart! Don’t forget to use walls to jump, avoid their abilities & beat’em up with your weapons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/8a8d18111dae1bfdcb742f8c38d27649.poster.avif?t=1769088471\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/8a8d18111dae1bfdcb742f8c38d27649.webm?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1495170/extras/8a8d18111dae1bfdcb742f8c38d27649.mp4?t=1769088471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OVERVIEW</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A colorful and unexpected experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 unique levels and 6 bosses </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different weapons for each level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple and smooth controls: you can use keyboard or a controller</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game modes: Normal and Hard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levels are filled with enemies who can only be defeated by jumping on them or using weapons like a boomerang or a laser gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the true ending by finishing the game in Hard mode!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks to ComiXme for their collaboration in the production of the trailer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
